lass=\"pl-c\">// Check directory existence before operations</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">dirExists</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">fsExistsSync</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./uploads<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-k\">if</span> (<span class=\"pl-k\">!</span><span class=\"pl-smi\">dirExists</span>) {\n  <span class=\"pl-en\">mkdirsSync</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./uploads<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h5>See:</h5><p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/fs.html#fs_fs_accesssync_path_mode\">https://nodejs.org/api/fs.html#fs_fs_accesssync_path_mode</a> - Node.js fs.accessSync documentation</p>\n"},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","line":149,"character":0,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts#L149"}],"parentId":1804}],"location":{"query":"node-utils/src.Variable.fsFuncs","hash":"fsExistsSync"}}},"is":{"declaration":true},"location":{"query":"node-utils/src.Variable.fsFuncs","hash":"fsExistsSync"},"text":{},"parentId":1804},{"id":1827,"name":"mkdirsSync","kind":4096,"kindString":"Property","flags":{},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","line":416,"character":2,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts#L416"}],"type":{"type":"reflection","declaration":{"id":1828,"name":"mkdirsSync","kind":65536,"kindString":"Type literal","flags":{},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","line":95,"character":16,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts#L95"}],"signatures":[{"id":1829,"name":"mkdirsSync","kind":4096,"kindString":"Call signature","flags":{},"comment":{"summary":[],"blockTags":[{"tag":"@function","content":[{"kind":"text","text":"mkdirsSync"}]},{"tag":"@description","content":[{"kind":"text","text":"同步递归创建目录，带错误处理。Synchronously creates directories recursively with comprehensive error handling and path validation."}]},{"tag":"@returns","content":[{"kind":"text","text":"如果目录创建成功返回true，否则返回false。True if directory creation succeeded, false otherwise"}]},{"tag":"@example","content":[{"kind":"code","text":"```ts\n// Create a simple directory\nconst success = mkdirsSync('./new-folder');\nconsole.log(success); // true\n\n```"}]},{"tag":"@example","content":[{"kind":"code","text":"```ts\n// Create nested directories\nconst created = mkdirsSync('./path/to/nested/folder');\nif (created) {\n  console.log('Directory structure created successfully');\n} else {\n  console.log('Failed to create directory structure');\n}\n\n```"}]},{"tag":"@example","content":[{"kind":"code","text":"```ts\n// Handle existing directories gracefully\nmkdirsSync('./existing-folder'); // Returns true if already exists\n```"}]}]},"parameters":[{"id":1830,"name":"dirPath","kind":32768,"kindString":"Parameter","flags":{},"comment":{"summary":[{"kind":"text","text":"要创建的目录路径（支持嵌套路径）。The directory path to create (supports nested paths)"}]},"type":{"type":"intrinsic","name":"string"},"text":{"comment":"<p>要创建的目录路径（支持嵌套路径）。The directory path to create (supports nested paths)</p>\n"}}],"type":{"type":"intrinsic","name":"boolean"},"is":{"declaration":false},"location":{"query":"node-utils/src.Variable.fsFuncs","hash":"mkdirsSync.__type"},"text":{"comment":"<h5>Function:</h5><p>mkdirsSync</p>\n<h5>Description:</h5><p>同步递归创建目录，带错误处理。Synchronously creates directories recursively with comprehensive error handling and path validation.</p>\n<h5>Returns:</h5><p>如果目录创建成功返回true，否则返回false。True if directory creation succeeded, false otherwise</p>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Create a simple directory</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">success</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">mkdirsSync</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./new-folder<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">success</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// true</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Create nested directories</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">created</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">mkdirsSync</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./path/to/nested/folder<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-k\">if</span> (<span class=\"pl-smi\">created</span>) {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Directory structure created successfully<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n} <span class=\"pl-k\">else</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Failed to create directory structure<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Handle existing directories gracefully</span>\n<span class=\"pl-en\">mkdirsSync</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./existing-folder<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Returns true if already exists</span>\n</code></pre>\n"},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/node-utils/src/fs/fsFuncs.ts","line":95,"character":0,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3